The lair of the black dragon
A dank square den, spacious and strewn with bones!
You can see the huge and ferocious black dragon.
There is only one way out: a flight of stairs leading up.
"Who is this that comes clomping down my staircase?" says the dragon, "Be gone or I'll spit my poison at you!"
> fold page into scorpion

> fold page into scorpion

You make the page into a scorpion.
No sooner have you completed the last fold, the scorpion springs to life! You drop it reflexively...
The scorpion's limbs flicker purposefully as it charges toward the hulking dragon. The scorpion stings the dragon once before it disappears under its huge black foot. The dragon gasps holding a ridgid pose before collapsing in a heap, stone dead!
> look at bones

> look at bones

They are all human, or humanoid. A lot of the skeletons are probably goblins, but some of the skulls look more man-like.
Amongst the bones is a golden crown!
With further searching you find a dragon's egg.
> take crown

> take crown

You pick it up.
