Unlocked.
The gate is pushed open and a mirror image of yourself charges fiercly through it towards you! You back away and turning to see where you are going, involuntarily start in fright... two more reflections of yourself are heading up the other two pathways! These then stop at the centre of the trees, where the three paths meet and you find yourself standing finally in the middle by the tree, with all the exits blocked by your dopplegangers. They press tightly against you until the four of you merge!

