> knock on white door

> knock on white door

With a swish, the two halves of the door seperate and stood between is a blue-skinned being arrayed in flaring white garments. His garments are blown about by a cool wind that issues forth from within the room.
'Who is this weakened wretch that taps feebly upon my door? Look at thee; thou art nought if not well within a hair's-breadth of death!'
By the merest raise of his hand, you fall limply into the room and lose consciousness for an unknown time..

A room from another world
You can see Urcon and a tall pedestal (containing an orb).
You can go out.
"My name is Urcon. I am going to heal thee somewhat with the merest wiggling of my fingers..." You now have 4 health points.
"I'm going away for a while - please do not touch my precious orb!" Urcon disappears in a burning flash!
